@killerdroid99 Incorrect. In memoized version, yes the max height of the tree remains the same BUT we maintain a table of values too. 
Please note that the memo (cache) object holds key of format m + ',' + n. How many combination you can imagine with this format? Answer: m * n.
The size of the memo table is m * n which is greater than m + n. So the space complexity is of order O(n*m).

